<section class="slide" id="multithreading">
	<h2>Wielowątkowość</h2>
	<p>
	<a href="http://developer.android.com/guide/practices/design/responsiveness.html">ANR - Application Not Responding</a>
	</p>
	<ol>Sposoby na wielowątkowość:
		<li><a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/java/lang/Thread.html">Thread/Runnable</a>
		<li><a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/os/Handler.html">Handler</a>
		<li><a href="http://developer.android.com/reference/android/view/View.html#post%28java.lang.Runnable%29">View.post*</a>
		<li><a href="http://developer.android.com/guide/topics/fundamentals/processes-and-threads.html#AsyncTask">AsyncTask</a>
	</ol>
	Więcej: <a href="http://developer.android.com/guide/topics/fundamentals/processes-and-threads.html">Process and Threads</a>
</section>


